    <title>消息轰炸</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/10/12/first/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/10/12/first/</id>
    <published>2022-10-12T03:27:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-10-12T15:47:54.407Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸炸</p><span id="more"></span><p>from pynput.keyboard import Key, Controller<br>import time<br>&#x2F;<em>注：发送前需要将键盘设置为英文输入模式！</em>&#x2F;<br>keyboard &#x3D; Controller()<br>a &#x3D; input(“请输入你需要循环输出的内容:”)<br>b &#x3D; eval(input(“请输入你想循环输出的次数:”))<br>print(“数据已接收, 请将光标移动到会话框”)<br>time.sleep(1)<br>for i in range(b):  # 设置发送次数<br>    keyboard.type(a)<br>    time.sleep(1)<br>    keyboard.press(Key.enter)<br>    keyboard.release(Key.enter)<br>print(‘消息发送完成!’)</p><h2 id="下载依赖包-pip-install-pynput"><a href="#下载依赖包-pip-install-pynput" class="headerlink" title="下载依赖包:pip install pynput"></a>下载依赖包:pip install pynput</h2><div class="note warning"><p>这里是警告。</p></div><div class="note info"><p>这里是提示</p></div>]]></content>
    
    
